<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="risk-vt">risk <strong><em>vt</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /rɪsk/    美 /rɪsk/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>冒...的危险；冒险干：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You <strong>risked</strong> your <strong>life</strong> to save the children. 
你冒着生命危险去救那些孩子。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>risk doing sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If you live abroad for some time you risk losing old friends in your homeland. 
如果在国外住一段时间，你可能会失去国内的老朋友。</p><footer>北师大④ – 12</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>risky /'rɪski/ adj   </p>
<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Young people may risk <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (go) deaf if they are exposed to very loud music every day.  （2013 上海改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. going  </p></div>